{"tid":35321,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］老老實實高進招變3仔係咪就係特異功能","createTime":"2016-12-12T04:26:06.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T15:52:59.000Z","uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63b0fc30dd420720ef2e798bfef16a1281b686fd","tid":35321,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:26:06.000Z","msg":"賭神1可見高進變3唔係千術換牌，而係變牌，但一樣係兩牌對調，只不過係透過意念集中，唔係衫袖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。仲提過呢招係最高境界，因為3仔係最細，要集中精神變一隻最廢既牌。<br />\n刀仔問點變，朱古力答師公話變就變，同賭聖一樣有師公輩既特異功能人物。<br />\n<br />\n假設係咁，賭神同賭聖單挑，賭神精通全部賭術出千加變3，賭聖用特異功能（可能變唔到3仔），咁邊個贏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66210dc05aed9aa8f29dd59cfd81f22840720ae2","tid":35321,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc3f5462c79b1beb1071942e0da15e687c409bbe","tid":35321,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b4564cd27490ff86dd57a84cc11c25f9bce15ed","tid":35321,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:47:09.000Z","msg":"00後無睇過賭神？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c70e84c6edce10c60c79cade09680279339bb","tid":35321,"uid":21533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:49:14.000Z","msg":"係啲人膠都廢事派比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57643a5b9a2c1a080d23813e815708686dfd670","tid":35321,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T04:57:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係啲人膠都廢事派比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas